{"description":"Intended to look like a styling photo shoot, this is my entry for the \"Snow White\" competition held by Design Connected. It was one of the three winners.","body":"<p>A very interesting experiment both style-wise and technically, inspired by the photography of photo stylist Paulina Arcklin. Since I have never worked with so many fabrics, nor have I done such purely white interiors, it forced me to find ways to differentiate between the numerous layers of “white” and get enough depth and character with a very limited palette.</p>\n<p>See the original Design Connected announcement <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/DesignConnected/photos/?tab=album&amp;album_id=506281409496814\">here</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"pics\">\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 1\" title=\"Picture 1\" src=\"/static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-1-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-1-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-1-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-1-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-1.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 2\" title=\"Picture 2\" src=\"/static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-2-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-2-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-2-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-2-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-2.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"pic\"><img class=\"lazyload image\" alt=\"Picture 3\" title=\"Picture 3\" src=\"/static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-3-20x20.jpg\" data-sizes=\"auto\" data-srcset=\"/static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-3-230x230.jpg 230w, /static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-3-460x460.jpg 460w\" data-src=\"/static/pics/t/snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-3-230x230.jpg\" data-gallery-item-src=\"snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-3.jpg\"></div>\n</div>\n","gallery":["snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-1.jpg","snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-2.jpg","snow-white-bedroom-styling-picture-3.jpg"]}